channel.title: USB Power from Eurorack to Axoloti?
channel.description:
I run a Eurorack modular synth and was wondering if this module puts out the right current in order to power the Axoloti via USB?
http://pulplogic.com/product/usb-power/
Power +12V: 10mA + load (plugged into USB @ 5V) Power -12V: 0mA (not used) Max load: 200mA (total between 2 ports)
Thanks for any help.
